              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Industry</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Emissions from manufacturing and construction, including cement, chemicals, food &amp; drink, iron &amp; steel production and non-energy use. </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
